Sun Mar 17 09:19:55 UTC 2024 - Dirk Müller <dmueller@suse.com>

- update to 0.5.2:
  * map: don't penalize failed insert/erase/find operations
  * str: add string comparison functions `cdada_str_ncmp` and
    `cdada_str_ncmp_c`
  * map: add `cdada_map_get_pos()`
